{"tid":1059600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【珠光寶氣】梅艷芳遺產撥款20幾萬擺壽酒 95歲梅媽收金壽桃金觀音","createTime":"2019-03-13T08:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T03:42:30.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":89,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"d13a80cf67e31905961be3536f68817bd0ff950f","tid":1059600,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T08:36:11.000Z","msg":"梅艷芳母親覃美金昨晚在尖沙嘴擺壽宴，大排筵席慶祝95歲生日，有網民在社交網晒壽宴相，着旗袍的梅媽一身貴氣，戴了珠鏈、耳環、玉戒指、手鏈、手鈪，還收到幾個金壽桃和金觀音做禮物，壽星梅媽笑得好開心。上月律師代表梅媽出庭，向法庭申請從梅艷芳遺產信託中，撥款20多萬元作擺壽酒之用，法官同意批出約25萬元壽宴費（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2HuAj83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HuAj83&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=2d1b1628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2HuAj83</a> ）。<br />\n有賓客在網上晒相片和短片，見到88歲黃夏蕙都有份出席壽宴，還拖着梅媽的雙手跳舞，兩位老人家雖然加埋183歲，但又扭又跳又轉圈，身體好硬朗，夏蕙姨更上台高歌《禪院鐘聲》助慶，有親友上前握着梅媽手送祝福，之後眾人齊齊唱生日歌，年邁的梅媽一面感動。<br />\n《蘋果》致電梅媽恭祝生日快樂，問到有甚麼願望？梅媽說：「多謝，梗係世界和平最好啦，大家都好，係咪？」梅媽透露正日生日是三月初十，問到昨晚擺幾多圍？梅媽說：「20幾圍囉。」收到好多金桃和金觀音？她笑說：「你又知，嘻嘻！」最鍾意哪份禮物？梅媽表示：「樣樣都鍾意，人哋送得出嚟，樣樣都鍾意啦。」問到是否玩得好開心？她說：「好開心，多謝你。」再問壽宴花了幾多錢？梅媽只說：「幾多錢都使咗啦。」是否兒子啟明埋單？她避答：「邊個埋單就埋咗啦，有乜好講唧。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190313/large/1552462092_f9ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190313%2Flarge%2F1552462092_f9ac.jpg&h=ab7f15d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190313/large/1552462092_e7b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190313%2Flarge%2F1552462092_e7b4.jpg&h=4a3a8578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190313/large/1552462092_bc28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190313%2Flarge%2F1552462092_bc28.jpg&h=f603e2f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190313/large/1552462093_5e3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190313%2Flarge%2F1552462093_5e3f.jpg&h=20d97622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190313/large/1552462093_ffe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190313%2Flarge%2F1552462093_ffe5.jpg&h=f053badd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190313/large/1552462094_e5ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190313%2Flarge%2F1552462094_e5ae.jpg&h=4e2b4505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190313/large/1552462094_c256.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190313%2Flarge%2F1552462094_c256.jpg&h=b0557060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190313/59363928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190313%2F59363928&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=662d0bdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190313%2F59363928&h=0bb10e41\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190313/59363928</a>"},{"pid":"9457e21566bfc44cc1d863473b7462ba623d4a5b","tid":1059600,"uid":103156,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T08:37:47.000Z","msg":"小心哽死"},{"pid":"dc190c851e9ed854fc01a4289591350e5f42f36c","tid":1059600,"uid":40763,"like":81,"dislike":2,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T08:43:09.000Z","msg":"梅姐埋左單都仲要埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj